Package model

Provides all classes for the controller component.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Assetable
    The Interface Assetable allows to get tiles from the model in the controller.
    Breakable
    The Interface IBreakable.
    ICharacter
    The Interface ICharacter allows to get the movements of the character in the controller.
    IDiamond
    The Interface IDiamond allows to get the movements of the diamonds in the controller.
    IEnemies
    The Interface IEnemies allows to get the movements of the enemies in the controller.
    IEntities
    The Interface IEntities allows to get the movements of the character and enemies in the controller.
    IMap
    The Interface IMap provides methods to change the reference numbers in the map.
    IModel
    The Interface IModel regroups the map attributes.
    IPosition
    The Interface IPosition provides positions in the map.
    IRock
    The Interface IRock allows to get the movements of the rocks in the controller.
    Movable
    The Interface Movable provides movement for all the tiles to the controller.
    Tilable
    The Interface Tilable provide a position and a reference for the tiles to the controller
